   </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Strategy</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Before I start getting bad reviews for over forty cards I have drawing engines for the entire game. I cycle multiple times in every game.<br>
<br>
Evil Evu:<br>
This decks set-up magi is Evil Evu. I use him that way I can draw massive amounts of cards and still have good attackers. Evil Evu has two of the greatest attack creatures for core. The Dark Furok can remove two creatures at once if the energy is there.<br>
<br>
Zet:<br>
Zet is the theft magi of this deck. I use Zet to take as many creatures as possible when he is revealed. The shadow cloak is nice to have out for my creatures. Zet has the ability to steal a creature every turn.<br>
<br>
Harror:<br>
Harror is the reset magi for this deck. If Zet gets through the first two magi of the opposing side then it&#39;s game. I play the cataclysm and nuke my hand with dark ayebaw to win. If not then I play as normal but use more destructive things.<br>
<br>
Special Considerations:<br>
Against Cataclysm: If I run into another cataclysm deck I use any of the energy removing creatures to finish off the magi. I also have the shadow cloak to use.<br>
<br>
Against Burrow: I can either turn it off with the belt or I can cataclysm.<br>
<br>
Against Wieney Swarms: I have the cataclysm and the core grag.<br>
<br>
Card Choices:<br>
Chaos Jile: I can attack little creatures to gain energy and turn off weakness.<br>
<br>
Core Grag: He&#39;s just to get rid of the Wieney swarms.<br>
<br>
Dark Furok: I have him in there to do alot of damage to two creatures.<br>
<br>
Chaos Plith: I use him to draw cards.<br>
<br>
Ugger: He&#39;s to do more damage whenattacking. Using the most out of my creatures energy.<br>
<br>
Shadow Cloak: He&#39;s to make sure that the discard people don&#39;t get to remove my creatures.<br>
<br>
Shadow Bones: This helps me do maximum damage to other creatures/ Magi.<br>
<br>
Turn: Duh Theft<br>
<br>
Vaporize: Just to get rid of relics Duh<br>
<br>
Rayje&#39;s Belt: Obviusly to get rid of those annoying effects/ powers<br>
<br>
Warriors Boots: Just for the extra damage/ sneak attack.<br>
<br>
Darkbreed Hyren: Just to keep order with the Hyren players.<br>
<br>
Cataclysm: Just to instant removal.<br>
<br>
Secrets of the Book: I use it just to have card drawing throughout the game.<br>
<br>
Entomb: To help lock down those annoying opposing spells.<br>
<br>
Harban: For the theft of the little guys without bother.<br>
<br>
Wudge: To make the opponent worry about the creatures he play.<br>
<br>
Koil: I use him to remove energy and get my discard back when I need it.<br>
<br>
Thanx or reading my deck I hope you like it and i hope it helps players play better. Thanx again Bye.<br>
